	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you're going to be doing changes to commercial games (e.g. romhacking), use an IPS patch (or similar binary patching methodology).  Do not upload ROM images directly:<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2018/07/nintendo-to-rom-sites-forget-cease-and-desist-now-were-suing/">https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2018/07/ ... ere-suing/</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://games.slashdot.org/story/18/07/23/1945241/nintendo-to-rom-sites-forget-cease-and-desist-now-were-suing">https://games.slashdot.org/story/18/07/ ... were-suing</a><!-- m -->

		

		</td>
	</tr>
